<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>403 | <%= siteName %></title>
    <style>
        body { margin: 0; background: #050505; color: white; font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; display: flex; flex-direction: column; height: 100vh; justify-content: center; align-items: center; overflow: hidden; }
        .error-code { font-size: 120px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0; color: #ff0055; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 15px rgba(255, 0, 85, 0.5)); animation: shake 0.5s infinite; }
        .error-message { font-size: 20px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); margin-bottom: 30px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .btn-back { padding: 12px 25px; border: 1px solid #ff0055; background: transparent; color: #ff0055; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; transition: 0.3s; }
        .btn-back:hover { background: #ff0055; color: white; box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 0, 85, 0.4); }
        @keyframes shake { 0% { transform: translateX(0); } 25% { transform: translateX(2px); } 50% { transform: translateX(-2px); } 75% { transform: translateX(2px); } 100% { transform: translateX(0); } }
        footer { position: absolute; bottom: 20px; font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4); }
        footer a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
        footer a:hover { color: #007bff; text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 4px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div style="text-align: center;">
        <h1 class="error-code">403</h1>
        <p class="error-message">Acceso Denegado. No tienes permisos.</p>
        <a href="/dash" class="btn-back">REGRESAR AL DASHBOARD</a>
    </div>
    <footer>
        Copyright &copy; 2026 <a href="<%= siteUrl %>" target="_blank"><%= siteName %></a>. All rights reserved.
    </footer>
</body>
</html>